170 PRINT: PRINT "I'M SORRY YOU DON'T LIKE IT THAT WAY.": GOTO 200
180 PRINT: PRINT "I KNEW YOU'D AGREE!!"
200 PRINT: PRINT "I REALLY ENJOYED MEETING YOU, ";SHOW(A);"."
210 PRINT "HAVE A NICE DAY!"
999 END

